title: Weight Watchers Lemon Pound Cak
directions: Preheat oven to 350*F. Spray the inside of the cake or bundt pan with Pam or other 0 point spray.
Combine cake mix, pudding mix, eggs, yogurt, 3/4 cup lemon juice and ¼ cup water. Whisk until combined. Do not overbeat.
Pour batter into cake pan and bake according to cake package instructions.
ingredients: 1 small package sugar free lemon pudding mix
